Hi everyone! I'm a B2B SaaS content marketer based in France. I'm a full-stack marketer but my favourite things are blogging and video editing! Currently I'm freelancing for some fab companies but I dream of working fully for just one company, one with great ethics ideally, as I like to get fully invested :grin:

Outside of work I'm a poet (couple of books published) and painter (first exhibition coming up, covid willing :crossed_fingers:)

If anyone wants to connect, my LinkedIn is here: <http://linkedin.com/in/ctrevien|linkedin.com/in/ctrevien>

Hey everyone! I’m Kirsten. I’m a freelance content marketing strategist, copywriter, and content writer. 

I mainly write for B2B tech (narrowed down to a few niches - such as MarTech, RetailTech, PropTech, HRtech, and FinTech - as well as more general B2B tech). I also write and strategise for marketing and e-commerce brands (B2B and B2C). 

Can’t think of any interesting facts about myself right now (evening brain fog!) - some boring ones are: mint chocolate chip is my fave ice cream and I never walk in the rain with an umbrella :relieved::umbrella_with_rain_drops:️ (despite living in Scotland). 

You can find me complaining and sometimes offering helpful tips on content marketing strategy, freelancing, and writing on LinkedIn: 

<https://www.linkedin.com/mwlite/in/b2bfreelance-content-marketing-strategist-and-writer|https://www.linkedin.com/mwlite/in/b2bfreelance-content-marketing-strategist-and-writer>
